                </p>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  <code
                    >VA tax before credits = tax from brackets on VA taxable
                    income</code
                  ><br />
                  <code
                    >Final VA tax = max(0, VA tax before credits − VA
                    credits)</code
                  >
                </p>
              </div>

