              <h3>
                Step‑by‑step: how this Virginia income tax calculator works
              </h3>
              <ol>
                <li>
                  <strong>You enter your annual gross income</strong> (ideally
                  your federal AGI).
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>We subtract your deduction</strong>: either the
                  Virginia standard deduction or your itemized deductions,
                  whichever you choose.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>We compute Virginia taxable income</strong> and apply
                  the four tax brackets to each slice of income.
                </li>
                <li>
                  <strong>We subtract any Virginia credits</strong> you entered
